[Latvia submitted its follow-up report no 5 to the OIE on Mon 21 Jul 2014. The report includes data of 9 new outbreaks, 7 in domestic swine and 2 in wild boars, located in 2 separate regions along the borders with Belarus (east, 7 outbreaks) and Estonia (north, 2 outbreaks). For the report, including a map, go to http://www.oie.int/wahis_2/public/wahid.php/Reviewreport/Review?page_refer=MapFullEventReport&reportid=15671.

The summary says:
Total outbreaks: 9
Total animals affected
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Wild boar: _Sus scrofa_ (Suidae) / not available / 4 / 3 / 1 / 0
Swine [domestic] / 134 / 10 / 6 / 128 / 0

